-Here I am again,
lost in the mountains.

6
00:01:47,633 --> 00:01:50,266
I suppose I should find
somewhere to sleep.

7
00:01:50,366 --> 00:01:51,333
[barking]

8
00:01:51,433 --> 00:01:53,733
-Those wild dogs are
going crazy tonight.

