13
00:02:08,333 --> 00:02:11,466
And besides not tasting
very good, if you eat me,

14
00:02:11,566 --> 00:02:13,900
you're going to get
seven year's bad luck.

15
00:02:15,133 --> 00:02:18,033
So don't make me hurt you.

16
00:02:18,133 --> 00:02:20,000
[cry]

17
00:02:20,100 --> 00:02:21,500
[crash]

