00:02:27,533 --> 00:02:29,066
-So what are you waiting for?

19
00:02:29,166 --> 00:02:30,933
Come and get me.

20
00:02:31,033 --> 00:02:32,833
[barking]

21
00:02:35,733 --> 00:02:36,333
-See?

22
00:02:36,433 --> 00:02:37,200
You're perfectly safe.

23
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:40,866
[meowing]

24
00:02:40,966 --> 00:02:43,066
-You saved my life.

25
00:02:43,166 --> 00:02:44,366
I'm so grateful.

26
00:02:44,466 --> 00:02:46,433
How can I ever repay you?

27
00:02:48,266 --> 00:02:49,800
-A ghost cat?

28
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:51,466
[music playing]

29
00:02:51,566 --> 00:02:53,133
