You're more shy than I am.

57
00:04:00,366 --> 00:04:03,333
Don't tell me you've never
had a girlfriend before.

58
00:04:03,433 --> 00:04:05,000
[laughter]

59
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:06,566
MAOMOLIN: I can't believe it.

60
00:04:06,666 --> 00:04:07,366
You're pathetic.

61
00:04:08,666 --> 00:04:10,800
Now I don't feel so bad.

62
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,166
-(SHOUTING) Shut up.

63
00:04:12,266 --> 00:04:14,666
If you're so smart, then how
come you haven't found a bride?

64
00:04:14,766 --> 00:04:15,233
Huh?

65
00:04:15,333 --> 00:04:16,066
