-Listen.

199
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,366
Thanks for coming out
on such short notice.

200
00:10:12,466 --> 00:10:14,400
There's something I've
been meaning to ask you.

201
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,700
