more than three,

206
00:10:22,833 --> 00:10:25,200
maybe five years at most.

207
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:27,400
-Do it soon or you're
going to miss your chance.

208
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:29,633
-Yeah.

209
00:10:29,733 --> 00:10:31,300
I know what you're thinking.

210
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,333
How can I trust a
loser like this?

211
00:10:33,433 --> 00:10:36,200
-Either do it or
don't, your moron.

212
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:36,741
-Huh?

213
00:10:38,566 --> 00:10:40,466
ACTOR AND RYOGA: What
I want is to marry you.

214
00:10:41,433 --> 00:10:42,466
ACTOR (ON TV): I'm serious.

215
00:10:42,566 --> 00:10:44,033
I can't live without you.

216
00:10:44,133 --> 00:10:45,433
What's the point to it?

217
00:10:45,533 --> 00:10:48,366
[music playing]

218
00:10:56,733 --> 00:10:57,633
-Akane.

219
00:10:57,733 --> 00:11:00,666
Please, would you marry me?

220
00:11:00,766 --> 00:11:02,366
[music playing]

221
